<br>
DD Power Ranking (dmg/second, and most efficiant DDs)<br>
<br>
1. Wizard<br>
2. Magician<br>
3. Druid<br>
4. Shaman and/or Enchanter<br>
5. Necromancer and/or Cleric<br>
<br>
DoT Power Ranking (dmg/mana, but over time)<br>
<br>
1. Necromancer (Should be almost all his power here)<br>
2. Shaman<br>
3. Druid and/or Enchanter<br>
4. Magician (can't believe they gave us a DoT)<br>
5. Clerics and Wizards (Wizards don't get DoTs do they?)<br>
<br>
<br>
